        <h2>Advertisement Policy</h2>
        <p>MilkDairy may display advertisements on the platform to support our services. These advertisements may be served by third-party ad networks, which may collect certain information to provide personalized ads.</p>
        <p>We may share non-personal data, such as device type, browser information, and usage statistics, with third-party ad networks to optimize and deliver relevant advertisements.</p>
        <p>You can manage your ad preferences through your browser settings or opt out of targeted advertising by visiting relevant ad network opt-out pages.</p>
        <p>Please note that clicking on any third-party advertisements may redirect you to external websites, which are not governed by this Privacy Policy. We encourage you to review their privacy policies before engaging with those services.</p>
      </section>
